00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,080
 You already know how term insurance works.

2
00:00:02,080 --> 00:00:05,680
 You pay the insurance company a small fee every year to protect your downside

3
00:00:05,680 --> 00:00:10,160
 and in the event of your passing, the insurance pays out a large sum of money to your family.

4
00:00:10,160 --> 00:00:14,160
 Today, I will tell you how you can enhance your base term policy

5
00:00:14,160 --> 00:00:19,200
 to increase its ability to protect you and your family better with something called as RIDERS.

6
00:00:19,200 --> 00:00:19,840
 By using...

7
00:00:21,760 --> 00:00:22,960
 PIZZAS!

8
00:00:22,960 --> 00:00:24,240
 Yep, I'm not kid...

9
00:00:25,760 --> 00:00:26,480
 Not kidding.

10
00:00:27,440 --> 00:00:30,320
 Your margarita is your base plan.

11
00:00:30,320 --> 00:00:31,920
 It covers your sum in short.

12
00:00:32,800 --> 00:00:33,440
 That's it.

13
00:00:33,440 --> 00:00:34,880
 Plain term plan.

14
00:00:34,880 --> 00:00:37,280
 Now, let's assume you want to enrich your plan.

15
00:00:37,280 --> 00:00:38,640
 This is where RIDERS come in.

16
00:00:38,640 --> 00:00:40,960
 You have several options in the market like...

17
00:00:40,960 --> 00:00:46,160
 Waiver of premium, critical illness, terminal illness, life stage benefit, zero cost option,

18
00:00:46,160 --> 00:00:49,520
 accidental death, accidental disability and so on.

19
00:00:49,520 --> 00:00:52,880
 And just like how not all toppings belong to your base plan...

20
00:00:53,520 --> 00:00:54,640
 Like your pineapple.

21
00:00:56,880 --> 00:00:59,840
 Not all RIDERS are necessary and recommended by us.

22
00:00:59,840 --> 00:01:01,600
 Let's say, accidental death rider.

23
00:01:01,600 --> 00:01:04,800
 By adding this rider to your base term insurance plan,

24
00:01:04,800 --> 00:01:09,600
 additional coverage is provided to the nominee the policy holder's death results from an accident.

25
00:01:09,600 --> 00:01:12,480
 This rider typically comes with a relatively affordable premium.

26
00:01:12,480 --> 00:01:16,080
 If you travel very frequently and seek additional accidental coverage,

27
00:01:16,080 --> 00:01:18,480
 opting for this very rider could be beneficial.

28
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:23,120
 However, at Ditto, we advise choosing a sufficient base cover with a good summer shot

29
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:28,240
 that provides coverage for all types of death, regardless of whether they are accidental or not.

30
00:01:31,520 --> 00:01:36,080
 Some insurers provide an extra benefit with the base cover of term insurance to address

31
00:01:36,080 --> 00:01:41,440
 total permanent disabilities and this is called income on permanent disability cover.

32
00:01:42,080 --> 00:01:46,560
 This additional benefit may be offered as a lump sum by some insurers,

33
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:50,160
 while others provide it as a monthly income for up to 10 years,

34
00:01:50,160 --> 00:01:52,560
 following a total permanent disability diagnosis.

35
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:56,240
 While the likelihood of experiencing permanent disabilities is low,

36
00:01:56,240 --> 00:01:59,440
 this add-on typically comes with an affordable premium.

37
00:01:59,440 --> 00:02:02,240
 According to Ditto, while it's not essential,

38
00:02:02,240 --> 00:02:06,480
 it could be beneficial to have this add-on for added financial security.

39
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:17,040
 Now, there are some toppings, say like your onions, that are mostly on most of the pizzas

40
00:02:17,040 --> 00:02:22,080
 and just like that, life stage benefit may be a part of your plan.

41
00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:25,840
 With this rider, you can increase the summer shot later in life,

42
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:31,680
 such as upon marriage or upon childbirth, when you have more number of dependents to look after.

43
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:36,000
 Some insurers also provide voluntary top-up options,

44
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:40,160
 allowing policyholders to increase coverage regardless of major life events.

45
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:50,000
 ICICI iProtect Smart, Tata AI Sampoon Raksha Plus, HDFC Care to Protect Smart and Bajaj E-Touch

46
